  "title": "ISic002992. Funerary inscription for Basil",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Francesca Prado; edition source: autopsy Prado 2023-05-09</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[Θ(εοῖς)] Χ(θονίοις) <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βασι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βασι\"><span data-text=\"Βασι\">Βασι</span></span></span>-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\">χαῖ]ρε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζη\n                    σες\">ἔζη-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[σες]</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\">[ἔτ]η</span> · κ·ε´ · <span data-text=\"καὶ\">καὶ</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span data-text=\"ἔνθα\">ἔνθα</span>  <span data-text=\"κατοικεῖς\">κ]ατοικεῖς</span>  <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span data-text=\"εἰς\">εἰς</span>  <span data-text=\"τοὺς\">τ]οὺς</span>  <span data-text=\"αἰῶ\n                    νες\">αἰῶ-<br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[νε]ς</span> ❦ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Francesca Prado; edition source: autopsy Prado 2023-05-09</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[..]Χ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βασι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βασι\"><span data-text=\"Βασι\">ΒΑΣΙ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\">...]ΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζη\n                    σες\">ΕΖΗ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[...</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\">..]Η</span>·Κ·Ε·<span data-text=\"καὶ\">ΚΑΙ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[......<span data-text=\"κατοικεῖς\">.]ΑΤΟΙΚΕΙΣ</span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[...<span data-text=\"τοὺς\">.]ΟΥΣ</span><span data-text=\"αἰῶ\n                    νες\">ΑΙΩ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[..]Σ</span>❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002992_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic002992_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002992.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic002992-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Prado from autopsy</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3326-3475\">Francesca Prado</a></p>  <p>To the spirts of the underworld. Farewell ... Basil... ! You lived for 25 years and you'll live here forever.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3326-3475\">Francesca Prado</a></p>  <p>Addio, degna Basil...! Vivesti 25 anni e qui abiti nei secoli.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Libertini 1949 96-97 no. 3 fig. 4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001865\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001865</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-6  20-25  Interlineation line 1 to 6  5-10  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
